de.upb.crc901.proseco.prototype.genderpredictor.htn

Class HTNCompositionStrategyRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.upb.crc901.proseco.prototype.genderpredictor.htn.HTNCompositionStrategyRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.upb.crc901.taskconfigurator.core.SolutionEvaluator, java.io.Serializable

    public class HTNCompositionStrategyRunner
extends java.lang.Object
implements de.upb.crc901.taskconfigurator.core.SolutionEvaluator
    This program searches the "inputs/classifierdef" folder of its execution for a file called "instances.serialized". This file is supposed to store a serialized object of the WEKA class Instances. It then invokes the AutoML machine to construct a good chain of WEKA tools. In a final step, this chain is serialized into Java code that is stored to "classifierdef" of the "outputs" folder
